text: Alexandr Vasyukhno (born 1 June 1997) is a Russian professional racing cyclist. He rode in the men's 1 km time trial event at the 2017 UCI Track Cycling World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
